initialDisplayPosts.title: What are Snippets in VSCode?
initialDisplayPosts.summary: Code snippets are templates that make it easier to enter repeating code patterns, such as loops or conditional-statements.

initialDisplayPosts.title: Removing sensitive data from the git history
initialDisplayPosts.summary: Its a bad practice to keep sensitive data like password in your repository. How can I remove that from previous commits (git history)?
